---
title: Carb Smart Crispy Chickpea Paneer and Chicken Salad with Cucumber and Honey-Tahini Drizzle
description: Golden seared paneer lends a salty, creamy bite to this fresh and bright chicken salad. Cucumber brings juicy sweetness, while chickpeas give texture and crunch!
